"{\"uid\": \"newschannel9.com-news-local-utcs-olivia-reeves-selected-to-us-olympic-weightlifting-team\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Now  43\\u00b0  Sat  48\\u00b0  Sun  53\\u00b0  byChuck Wasserstrom | UTC Staff  CHATTANOOGA, Tenn. -University of Tennessee at Chattanooga student Olivia Reeves has been announced as one of the five athletes representing USA Weightlifting during this summer's Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 52, \"end\": 55, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Tennessee_at_Chattanooga\", \"score\": 0.9999454160831686, \"rank\": 5.458687850348312e-05, \"text\": \"UTC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Tennessee_at_Chattanooga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Tennessee_at_Chattanooga\"}, {\"begin\": 97, \"end\": 106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Tennessee\", \"score\": 0.9350871791692498, \"rank\": 0.06887939322674341, \"text\": \"Tennessee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Tennessee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Tennessee\"}, {\"begin\": 130, \"end\": 136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Pope\", \"score\": 0.7273757253500878, \"rank\": 0.37427027628912574, \"text\": \"Olivia\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Pope\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Pope\"}, {\"begin\": 204, \"end\": 221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Weightlifting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USA Weightlifting\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Weightlifting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Weightlifting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The announcement took place Friday in Colorado Springs, Colorado.\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 303, \"end\": 311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado_Buffaloes\", \"score\": 0.5388152086524728, \"rank\": 0.5570226766606448, \"text\": \"Colorado\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado_Buffaloes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado_Buffaloes\"}, {\"begin\": 321, \"end\": 329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado_Buffaloes\", \"score\": 0.5388152086524728, \"rank\": 0.5570226766606448, \"text\": \"Colorado\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado_Buffaloes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado_Buffaloes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Click here for the USA Weightlifting announcement.\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reeves, who competes at 71 kg, is joined on the U.S. squad by Jourdan Delacruz (49 kg), Wes Kitts (102 kg), Hampton Morris (61 kg) and Mary Theisen-Lappen (+81 kg).\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 445, \"end\": 452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Jourdan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.201343409332423e-14, \"text\": \"Jourdan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Jourdan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Jourdan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic weightlifting competition will take place Aug. 7-11 at the South Paris Arena.\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 552, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_weightlifting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic weightlifting\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_weightlifting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_weightlifting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reeves, a senior majoring in sociology, is looking to become the first UTC currently-enrolled student to participate in the Olympic Games-and is believed to be the first student in the University's 138-year history to be selected for an Olympic team-something she said feels \\\"monumental.\\\"\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 927, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 710, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Tennessee_at_Chattanooga\", \"score\": 0.9999454160831686, \"rank\": 5.458687850348312e-05, \"text\": \"UTC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Tennessee_at_Chattanooga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Tennessee_at_Chattanooga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the final Olympic qualifying event in Phuket, Thailand, in April, the Hixson native won three gold medals while setting a trio of American records (118 kg snatch, 150 kg clean and jerk, 268 kg total).\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 970, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\", \"score\": 0.9999371468767637, \"rank\": 6.285676063952608e-05, \"text\": \"Phuket\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\"}, {\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_under-23_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8372974007009629, \"rank\": 0.10505515476156708, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_under-23_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_under-23_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1002, \"end\": 1008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hixson_High_School\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.923682266679484e-14, \"text\": \"Hixson\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hixson_High_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hixson_High_School\"}, {\"begin\": 1062, \"end\": 1070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9971400087224055, \"rank\": 0.002864231729292868, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The soft-spoken athlete is not one to boast about her accomplishments at school, but it also has not fully sunk in yet that she will be an Olympian.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1273, \"end\": 1281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999078695337871, \"rank\": 9.213895011514469e-05, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reeves will arrive in Paris on July 18, where she will spend nearly a month as the competitions take place.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1306, \"end\": 1311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999896393042158, \"rank\": 1.0360803133351152e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She will compete at 7:30 p.m. Paris time (1:30 p.m. in Chattanooga) on Friday, Aug. 9.\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1422, \"end\": 1427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999896393042158, \"rank\": 1.0360803133351152e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During her time there, she plans to stay busy with training, exploring the Olympic Village, watching as many sporting events as she can and making friends.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999995013695, \"rank\": 4.986300816459843e-10, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To learn more about Reeves' journey to the U.S. Olympic team, visitUTC News.\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2025Sinclair, Inc.\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1733, \"entities\": []}]}"